# Local-only backup snapshots (NEVER commit — exceed GitHub's 100 MB/file limit).
# Restore tarballs live in /app/memory/backups/ but the MANIFEST.md IS committed.
memory/backups/*
!memory/backups/MANIFEST.md
!memory/backups/.gitkeep
*.tar.gz
